"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Healthy gingiva in a 6-year-old child",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 324px; height: 229px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    No plaque is visible on the teeth at the gingival margin (gum line). The gingiva is uniformly pink without redness or edema.",
